characterCustomizations.biography:
GM of the Mythic raiding guild Idiokracy

-Idiokracy- 8/8 Heroic, 4/8 Mythic EP, 7/9 Mythic BoD is recruiting quality raiders to progress through Mythic Azshara's Palace! Raid times are T&Th 8-11PM PST. All roles are considered for quality players! Friendly guild. Usually achieve AOTC in first week then progress through Mythic. Only six hours of raid time so we make the best of a short schedule and are one of the top 6 hours guilds on our realm. Comprised of many CE quality players who don't want to raid 9-12 hours a week.

Bnet: StickOButter#11368

Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/Stick_O_Butter - I stream our raids on occasion to share the good times!
